short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Track ticket price history on Gotogate.com

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,es,e:
Gotogate Price Tracker is an extension for Gotogate.com. With it you can check price history of airlines.

Gotogate is a trademark of Gotogate, Inc. This extension was not created or endorsed by Gotogate, Inc
If you have any questions or suggestions, please feel free to contact us:
https://www.aliprice.com/information/index?page=contact

By installing the AliPrice extension, you accept the terms of the "AliPrice Terms of Service" and allow the extension to redirect to Gotogate affiliate program links. AliPrice Terms of Service - https://www.aliprice.com/information/index/page/term_of_use
